OL,7,FThe Presbyterian Church is coming
OL,8,Funder increasing pressure to hold an
OL,9,Findependent inquiry into the
OL,10,Fsafeguarding scandal that has plunged
OL,11,Fthe church into crisis.
OL,13,FThe Moderator of the Presbyterian
OL,14,FChurch in Ireland, Rev Dr Trevor
OL,15,FGribben is to resign over a catalogue
OL,16,Fof serious and significant
OL,17,Fsafeguarding failings.
OL,19,FA convicted paedophile is at the heart
OL,20,Fof the scandal which continues to rock
OL,21,Fthe Presbyterian Church.
