OL,7,FUTV has discovered who he is but won't
OL,8,Freveal his name to protect the
OL,9,Fidentity of young victims and anyone
OL,10,Felse potentially exposed to risk.
OL,12,FHe was a voluntary youth leader
OL,13,Fconnected to a church. Earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, he was jailed for sexually
OL,15,Fabusing children.
OL,17,FThe offences are not linked to the
OL,18,Fchurch or his youth work.
