OL,7,FIt was only when police made contact
OL,8,Fabout him did alarm bells ring within
OL,9,Fthe Presbyterian Church, prompting an
OL,10,Finternal review spanning a thirteen-
OL,11,Fyear period.
OL,13,FIt's understood PSNI investigations
OL,14,Fare now focused on the serious
OL,15,Fsafeguarding failures uncovered.
OL,17,FCrisis continues to engulf the
OL,18,FPresbyterian Church, despite the
OL,19,Funprecedented resignation of its
OL,20,Fleader.
