OL,7,FRev Dr Trevor Gribben announced his
OL,8,Fresignation as moderator earlier this
OL,9,Fweek when revelations were made at a
OL,10,Fpress conference.
OL,12,FThey have been described as a "sick
OL,13,Fpantomime" by a Presbyterian.
OL,15,FLaurence Kirkpatrick settled a legal
OL,16,Fcase after he was sacked by the
OL,17,FPresbyterian Church from the Union
OL,18,FTheological College in 2019.
